                    <ab>(C.) In nomine sancte et individue trinitatis. <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/239">Otto</persName> divina favente clementia Romanorum <rs
                            key="#Emperor/king">imperator</rs> augustus. Si ecclesiarum dei curam
                        gerimus easque dilatare studuerimus, nostri imperii fastigium augmentari
                        minime diffidimus. Quocirca omnibus sancte dei ecclesie fidelibus
                        presentibus ac futuris notum esse volumus, qualiter interventu ac petitione
                        nostri dilecti ducis Ottonis <rs key="#Patriarchs">patriarcha</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Castle #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Immunity #Mother_churches #Patriarchs"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/92"><rs key="#Mother_churches">sancte
                                Aquilegiensis ecclesie</rs></orgName>
                        <persName key="#Patriarchs" ref="#people/651">Rodaldus</persName> nostram
                        humiliter adiit celsitudinem, deprecans quatinus nos pro dei amore nostreque
                        anime remedio nostre auctoritatis preceptali pagina sancte Aquilegiensi
                        ecclesie in honore beate Marie edificate <rs key="#Castle">quinque
                            castella</rs> ipsius basilice nominative que propria ipsius ecclesie
                        sunt: <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Census #Profits_of_justice #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Landed_possessions #Wine #Hay/fodder #Cereals #Immunity #Rivers #Mills #Slave #Aldius"
                            ref="#places/951"><geogName
                                key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Census #Profits_of_justice #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Landed_possessions #Wine #Hay/fodder #Cereals #Immunity #Rivers #Mills #Slave #Aldius"
                                ref="#estates/548"><rs
                                    key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                    >Buga</rs></geogName></placeName>, <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Census #Profits_of_justice #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Landed_possessions #Wine #Hay/fodder #Cereals #Immunity #Rivers #Mills #Slave #Aldius"
                            ref="#places/952"><geogName
                                key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Census #Profits_of_justice #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Landed_possessions #Wine #Hay/fodder #Cereals #Immunity #Rivers #Mills #Slave #Aldius"
                                ref="#estates/549"><rs
                                    key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                    >Phagangna</rs></geogName></placeName>, <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Census #Profits_of_justice #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Landed_possessions #Wine #Hay/fodder #Cereals #Immunity #Rivers #Mills #Slave #Aldius"
                            ref="#places/953"><geogName
                                key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Census #Profits_of_justice #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Landed_possessions #Wine #Hay/fodder #Cereals #Immunity #Rivers #Mills #Slave #Aldius"
                                ref="#estates/550"><rs
                                    key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                    >Croang</rs></geogName></placeName>, <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Census #Profits_of_justice #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Landed_possessions #Wine #Hay/fodder #Cereals #Immunity #Rivers #Mills #Slave #Aldius"
                            ref="#places/954"><geogName
                                key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Census #Profits_of_justice #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Landed_possessions #Wine #Hay/fodder #Cereals #Immunity #Rivers #Mills #Slave #Aldius"
                                ref="#estates/551"><rs
                                    key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                    >Vdene</rs></geogName></placeName>, <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Census #Profits_of_justice #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Landed_possessions #Wine #Hay/fodder #Cereals #Immunity #Rivers #Mills #Slave #Aldius"
                            ref="#places/955"><geogName
                                key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Census #Profits_of_justice #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Landed_possessions #Wine #Hay/fodder #Cereals #Immunity #Rivers #Mills #Slave #Aldius"
                                ref="#estates/552"><rs
                                    key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                    >Braitan</rs></geogName></placeName>, ex unoquoque castello
                        circiter per ambitum ex omnique parte sicut tres miliarii continent <rs
                            key="#Profits_of_justice">placita</rs>, ut praedictus patriarcha
                        custodiret in omni parte eorum castrorum miliariis tribus, et ab hominibus
                        infra ipsos miliarios tres <rs key="#Census">censum</rs> acciperet atque <rs
                            key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">herbaticum</rs> ex omnibus
                        animalibus ibidem pascentibus tolleret, ut magis domino darentur quam malis
                        vastatoribus. Cuius dignis postulationibus aures nostre pietatis
                        accomodantes corroboramus et firmamus eidem ecclesie atque patriarchis ibi
                        pro tempore constitutis prenominata castra cum omnibus pertinentiis tres
                        tenentibus miliarios, ut homines infra hunc terminum habitantes ad nullum
                        placitum et ad nullam districtionem eant nisi ad patriarchalem potenciam
                        neque alicui censum reddant, neque ullus herbaticum homo tollat, sed cuncta
                        que infra ipsius terminum loci sunt, in ipsius potestate suorumque
                        successorum sint, omni contradictione et diminoratione penitus remota.
                        Insuper eciam concedimus et confirmamus eidem ecclesie+ sive patriarchis ibi
                        pro tempore ordinatis prenominatum terminum cum omnibus<rs
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie"> villis massariciis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs>
                        <rs key="#Wine">vineis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Hay/fodder">pratis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Cereals">campis cultis</rs> et incultis <rs key="#Rivers">aquis
                            aquarumque decursibus</rs>
                        <rs key="#Mills">molendinis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Slave">servis et ancillis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Aldius">aldionibus et aldionabus</rs> seu cum omnibus rebus
                        mobilibus et inmobilibus que dici vel nominari possunt, ut habeant
                        potestatem in eodem loco placita custodiendi vel quicquid eorum voluntas
                        decreverit faciendi. Precipientes denique precipimus iubendo ut <rs
                            key="#Immunity">nullus dux marchio episcopus comes vicecomes nullaque
                            nostri regni magna vel parva persona</rs> predictum patriarcham suosque
                        successores de prenominatis finibus sive castris vel quicquid in ipsius
                        locis ad congruentem utilitatem eidem patriarche suisque successoribus
                        molestare disvestire inquietare vel per placita fatigare sine legali iudicio
                        audeat vel presumat, sed firmiter liceat eis et potenter tenere et in eisdem
                        locis omnem districtionem tenere, omnium hominum controversia penitus
                        sublata. Si quis igitur huius nostre auctoritatis paginam violaverit, quod
                        minime credimus fieri, sciat se compositurum <rs key="#Penalty">auri
                            purissimi libras mille</rs>, mediedatem <rs key="#Camera_regis">kamere
                            nostre</rs> et medietatem prefate ecclesie+ sive patriarchis. Quod ut
                        verius credatur diligentiusque ab omnibus observetur, sigilli nostri
                        impressione hanc paginam propria manu corroborantes inferius eandem iussimus
                        sigillare. Signum domni Ottonis secundi serenissimi inperatoris (M.) et
                        invictissimi augusti. <persName key="#Chancellor"><name ref="Adalbertus"
                                >Adelbertus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Chancellor">cancellarius</rs> advicem <persName
                            key="#Archchancellor #Bishops" ref="#people/223">Petri</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopi</rs> et <rs key="#Archchancellor"
                            >archicancellarii</rs> recognovi et subscripsi. Data III. idus iun. anno
                        dominice incarnationis DCCCCLXXXIII, indictione XI, regni vero domni secundi
                        Ottonis XXVI, imperii quoque eius XVI; actum <placeName ref="#places/59"
                            >Verone</placeName>; feliciter amen.</ab>
                </div>
